metadata.name: Amberlina
metadata.description:
Thank you for choosing the Puppet Workshop! 

Care Instructions:

Feed your puppet.

Provide your puppet with a sleeping area, preferably something compact.

Please provide your puppet with constant activities. Failure to do some may result in mayhem related mischief. 

Finally, all repairs to your puppet are the responsibility of the owner. 

(The Puppet Workshop is not responsible for damage caused by your puppet, it is the advise of the Workshop that you increase all insurances immediately.)
